ZH: 我大约需要五分钟做完这个任务。
EN: It will take me about five minutes to finish this task.

ZH: 他大约二十岁左右。
EN: He is about twenty years old.

ZH: 明天大约会下雨。
EN: It will rain tomorrow, approximately.

ZH: 这本书大约有五百页。
EN: This book has about five hundred pages.

ZH: 我大约每周去一次健身房。
EN: I go to the gym about once a week.

ZH: 他大约明年会去留学。
EN: He will study abroad about next year.

ZH: 这个问题大约在三天前被解决了。
EN: This problem was solved about three days ago.

ZH: 飞机大约晚点了一个小时。
EN: The plane was about an hour late.

ZH: 我大约需要八个小时才能到达那里。
EN: It will take me about eight hours to get there.

ZH: 这种药大约需要两个星期才能见效。
EN: This medicine will take about two weeks to work.

ZH: 那个男人大约有一米八的个子。
EN: That man is about 1.8 meters tall.

ZH: 这种电脑大约能使用五年。
EN: This computer can be used for about five years.

ZH: 我们大约还有十分钟就到了。
EN: We are about ten minutes away.

ZH: 这个城市的人口大约有一百万。
EN: The population of this city is about one million.

ZH: 让我想一想，大约五分钟。
EN: Let me think for about five minutes.

ZH: 太阳大约在东方升起。
EN: The sun rises in the east, approximately.

ZH: 你大约几点离开家的？
EN: What time did you leave home, approximately?

ZH: 这个问题大约在三点钟被解决了。
EN: This problem was solved around three o'clock.

ZH: 我大约上个月买的这件衣服。
EN: I bought this piece of clothing about last month.

ZH: 这里有大约一千人参加了活动。
EN: There were about a thousand people attending the event.
